      "description": "Available is an investment-grade 2008 BMW M3 (E92) in pristine Alpine White. This example features the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering linear power to an 8,400 RPM redline through a precise longitudinal 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanically, the vehicle is superlative: preventative rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator services are fully documented. The chassis remains taut with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) functioning perfectly, while the M Variable Differential Lock ensures optimal torque vectoring across the rear axle. Every body panel retains factory tolerances with original VIN tags intact. Inside, the Novillo leather remains supple with zero bolster compression or wear. This is a turn-key, high-revving masterpiece for the discerning purist seeking an unmolested, showroom-quality icon.",
